Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.00,0:01:13.79,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}You changed me so much I don't remember what I was like before we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.17,0:01:18.26,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}The breeze caresses our cheeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.26,0:01:20.26,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Lullaby of Birdland...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.64,0:01:24.60,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}As we run down the slope,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.77,0:01:28.52,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}our flimsy shadows extend.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.52,0:01:33.44,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}It's like a neverending summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.44,0:01:39.24,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}It feels like when we snuck into the pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.24,0:01:45.16,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Yeah, let's swim with our clothes on. Jump in!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.49,0:01:47.83,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}It's an intense spiral of temptation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.25,0:01:52.33,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}A beat pierces my heart. A strange one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.83,0:01:56.05,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}It vanishes after a quick spark.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.05,0:01:58.84,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Even on bad days, I dress up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.84,0:02:03.72,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}and dance to some swing. The music quickly surrounds me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.72,0:02:06.56,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}What is this dance exactly? I can't stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.56,0:02:15.82,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Don't leave me. It's stuck in my head, and I can't get it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.23,0:02:18.90,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}The melody...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.66,0:02:24.70,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}is like love.
