Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.02,0:00:23.85,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Hey there! Well don't you look chipper!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.85,0:00:27.12,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Are you that happy about being in \Nclass 10 with all the rowdy kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.11,0:00:31.30,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.30,0:00:32.55,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.06,0:00:40.14,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,He isn't used to being in a different class than his friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.14,0:00:42.33,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,This is his first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.20,0:00:51.95,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Um, you've got a petal in your hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.95,0:00:53.61,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,That's okay. I'll get it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.89,0:02:40.13,apollon main,Maruo,0,0,0,,Nishimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.40,0:02:43.14,apollon main,Maruo,0,0,0,,I'm so happy we're in the same class again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:44.07,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.07,0:02:45.79,apollon main,Maruo,0,0,0,,Th-That's cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.80,0:02:47.77,apollon main,,0,0,0,,We just did our self introductions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.65,0:02:49.48,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.13,0:02:54.38,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You got his ticket for the sleeper car too, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.38,0:02:56.22,apollon main,Maruo,0,0,0,,S-Sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.22,0:02:58.19,apollon main,Maruo,0,0,0,,He said to keep it a secret from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.77,0:03:01.82,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Because of that, I had a nice trip. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.35,0:03:07.16,apollon main,Boy,0,0,0,,It's finally over!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.16,0:03:10.46,apollon main,Boy,0,0,0,,We should've decided the class rep by drawing lots in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.46,0:03:11.83,apollon main,Boy,0,0,0,,No kiddin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.07,0:03:14.71,apollon main,Boy,0,0,0,,Hey, I heard there was already a fight in class 10!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.76,0:03:18.06,apollon main,Boy,0,0,0,,I'm just glad I wasn't put in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.67,0:03:28.22,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Hey, you done already, boxing club?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.80,0:03:31.42,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,I thought you'd have a little more spirit than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.42,0:03:32.92,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.92,0:03:34.59,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Hi, Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.59,0:03:36.20,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Don't give me "Hi"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.20,0:03:39.82,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Why are you fighting on the first day of school?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:42.36,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Just gettin' a little exercise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.30,0:03:46.19,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,That was fun. Been too long since I had a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.19,0:03:47.70,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Hey, Sen! Are you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.09,0:03:48.99,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:50.80,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.81,0:04:03.84,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,W-Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.21,0:04:06.12,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.12,0:04:06.68,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.20,0:04:09.55,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You're going over there with that banged-up face?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.48,0:04:11.68,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Is it that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:12.88,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Ri.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.53,0:04:17.61,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sorry, but would you take this guy to the nurse's office and patch him up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:21.11,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,All right, get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.41,0:04:24.00,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Ri, he's in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.00,0:04:24.86,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:30.37,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,It still hurts a little,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.99,0:04:33.08,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,but I should get used to it eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.18,0:04:38.41,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,The pain will go away, and I'll be able to relax and smile again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.93,0:04:45.79,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,I'm going to submit this painting to this year's public exhibition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.79,0:04:48.30,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,This is the one Sentaro modeled for.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.09,0:04:52.39,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Um... Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.39,0:04:53.86,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,Oh, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.86,0:04:56.54,apollon main,,0,0,0,,You don't have to force yourself to give me feedback.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:05:00.32,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,S-Sorry. I don't know much about art.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.32,0:05:03.82,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,Oh? That's a strange thing for you to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.96,0:05:08.87,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,After all, painting and jazz are relatively close cousins, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:12.69,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,A painting is created on a space called the canvas,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.69,0:05:15.12,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,while jazz is created during a time called the performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.12,0:05:19.88,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,It's like etching your living self into that place and time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.81,0:05:23.62,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,Or something like that.\NI was only repeating someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.62,0:05:27.51,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,Junichi was talking about that \Nwhen I went down to the basement.
