Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:30.01,apollon main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)\c&H010209&\shad0\bord0\fs30\blur0.75\fnOld newspaper font\b0\frz71.121\clip(m 1011 419 l 969 396 891 580 980 590)\pos(967,477)}Fukahori Yurika
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:30.01,apollon main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)\c&H010209&\shad0\bord0\fs30\blur0.75\fnOld newspaper font\b0\pos(830,448)\frz62.54\clip(m 865 389 l 770 472 753 530 824 546)}Fukahori Yurika
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.52,0:05:33.51,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,It's very interesting to listen to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.13,0:05:36.28,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,I'd like to talk to him more about all kinds of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:42.48,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Um, I went to Tokyo during spring break.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:47.29,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I dropped by his boarding house, but he wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.29,0:05:49.03,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,Oh, that's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.03,0:05:51.57,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Apparently, he hadn't been back for a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.57,0:05:54.54,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,so there were a lot of letters stuffed in his mail slot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:05:58.83,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Someone said he might be staying at another person's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.20,0:06:01.34,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.87,0:06:05.09,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,One of those letters may have been important.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.02,0:06:08.13,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,I wonder where he went.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.24,0:06:14.66,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Aren't you done yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.66,0:06:17.22,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Just put a little spit on cuts like these and they'll heal up fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.22,0:06:19.06,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,What'll you do if it gets infected?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.06,0:06:20.89,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Come on, close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.28,0:06:26.15,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.81,0:06:31.91,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Ri'ko, I'm glad you're in the same class as Richie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.99,0:06:37.16,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,From now on, would you look after him for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:43.48,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Um, well, I'd better get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.48,0:06:47.17,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Richie! Glad I caught up to \Nyou before you went home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:51.01,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Are those tears?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:54.93,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,This glob looks like a tear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.83,0:06:58.06,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,That's the tear of a broken heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.51,0:07:01.35,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,In Greek mythology, the god Apollo
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:04.54,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,fell in love with Daphne, \Nthe daughter of a river god.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.54,0:07:08.28,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,He became obsessed and chased her all around, but she wouldn't stop running.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:11.65,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,At last, she gave Apollo \Nthe ultimate rejection
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.65,0:07:14.12,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,by turning into a bay laurel tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:16.91,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,What an awful case of heartbreak!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.21,0:07:18.44,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,Of course he would cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.44,0:07:22.21,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,He was so grief-stricken that he fashioned a wreath out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:23.92,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Who...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:24.71,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Who's he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.89,0:07:28.84,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,This is Matsuoka Seiji, \Na second-year student.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:30.82,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,He's the great hope of East High's art club.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.82,0:07:34.27,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,Oh, stop it! You're embarrassing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.27,0:07:35.97,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,Kawabuchi Sentaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.42,0:07:38.47,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,We're both in class 10, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:40.48,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.46,0:07:46.55,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Richie, do you remember that guy from last year?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.55,0:07:47.44,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.06,0:07:49.64,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,I'm gettin' the chills.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.64,0:07:51.65,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right, Sentaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:54.82,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,Are you free on our next day off?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:57.74,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,I want to get you a present as thanks for being my model.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.88,0:08:04.75,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait up! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:07.59,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Idiot! Apollo, my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.97,0:08:11.27,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I could never see this guy wearing a laurel wreath!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.59,0:08:23.39,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Ri, do you have detention?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.90,0:08:27.78,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Yeah. I forgot my math homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.78,0:08:30.34,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,That's unusual for someone as level-headed as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:35.03,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Who said I was level-headed? \NI'm careless as can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.34,0:08:38.53,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I get more absent-minded in the spring, but I better snap out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.36,0:08:40.88,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,This song...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.88,0:08:43.27,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,It's from "The Sound of Music."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.15,0:08:47.04,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I love this song.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:50.77,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Yeah, I figured you would like that movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.77,0:08:53.58,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Oh, no, I didn't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.58,0:08:55.90,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I wanted to, but before I knew it, it'd already stopped playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.64,0:08:58.52,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I bet it was a good movie, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.52,0:09:00.06,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,How could I miss it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.64,0:09:04.31,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I guess I thought I'd be able to see it anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:06.74,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I'm pretty dumb, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:22.20,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,What is that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:24.08,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,"My Favorite Things."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:25.58,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.47,0:09:45.93,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Better not. I had my shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.03,0:09:50.56,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, there was somethin' I wanted your advice about, Richie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:53.19,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,About... my date.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.05,0:09:56.01,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,With Yurika?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.01,0:09:57.17,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:10:02.89,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll give the perfect advice for a romantic beginner like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:05.03,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Don't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:07.50,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:09.42,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Huh? What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.42,0:10:13.74,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,On a one-on-one date, you're sure to freeze up and blow the whole deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.74,0:10:15.60,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,D-Don't make fun of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.60,0:10:17.76,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,I can handle a date, piece of cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.19,0:10:21.15,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Oh, sure! You really think \Nyou can keep TPO in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.15,0:10:23.91,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,in front of that princess and behave accordingly?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.91,0:10:25.02,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,T-TP?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:27.74,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You know what it is? You don't, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.74,0:10:30.15,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,But for your own sake, you better not go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.22,0:10:32.39,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,TP...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.88,0:10:37.15,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Man, what a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.77,0:10:40.85,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I wish everyone would just stop falling in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.15,0:10:52.00,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,That idiot! Well, don't blame me for what happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.68,0:11:07.73,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,Sentaro, don't hold back. Tell me if you see something you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.01,0:11:13.27,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Oh, nah. I never get expensive stuff like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.27,0:11:16.40,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Even this jacket is a hand-me-down from Jun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:18.44,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.63,0:11:24.74,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,And from then on, he was all we talked about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.88,0:11:31.09,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Jun used to be the coolest kid in his high school!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.09,0:11:33.71,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,He was good at fightin', smart too...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.71,0:11:35.79,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.79,0:11:37.55,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,We had a good time talkin' about him,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:41.70,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,but now all I got left is a feelin' of emptiness in the pit of my stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.70,0:11:43.05,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Sen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.60,0:11:45.31,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Did your date go well?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.31,0:11:47.50,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,C-Course it did!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.50,0:11:51.98,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,That's right. A date is a piece of cake for you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.45,0:11:54.31,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:55.40,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.65,0:12:00.11,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,It didn't go well at all, did it? Just like I predicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.63,0:12:04.37,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sen, stay away from her from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:08.08,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,What makes you say that all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:13.56,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You really are dense, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.56,0:12:17.50,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Any way you look at it, you and a refined girl like that just don't match up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.15,0:12:20.22,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,She's out of your league.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:27.35,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Crap. I went too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.78,0:12:33.47,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,Hi, Kawabuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.73,0:12:35.44,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.79,0:12:39.00,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,I heard you went on a date with Yurika?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.00,0:12:42.53,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,She said she had a great time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.53,0:12:45.36,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,H-Hey, is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:47.53,apollon main,,0,0,0,,Did she say anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.53,0:12:48.75,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,You wanna know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.01,0:12:54.16,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,Uh-huh! She said you were handsome
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.52,0:12:56.81,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,and that maybe she'll hold your hand next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.81,0:12:57.33,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.21,0:13:04.22,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Oh, you're already here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:08.76,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Hey, you wanna try playin'\N"My Favorite Things" again together?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.47,0:13:13.73,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,What's this? I thought he'd be mad at me for what I said at lunch,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.32,0:13:16.40,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,but he seems to be in a great mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.06,0:13:21.12,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Hey, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.99,0:13:24.45,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I thought only jazz was allowed in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.73,0:13:29.45,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Oh, that kid with the bowl cut, Matsuoka, forced it on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.04,0:13:32.64,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,I couldn't refuse, so I just carried it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.92,0:13:36.42,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Wh-What's that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.36,0:13:41.46,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Good for you, making a nice friend that lends you records.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.87,0:13:44.21,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,Hey, Sen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.21,0:13:45.98,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,Would you come upstairs a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.98,0:13:47.39,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.22,0:13:50.73,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,What, did a new record come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.73,0:13:52.60,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,Just come up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:53.22,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.29,0:13:57.73,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Is he going to listen to that record?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.38,0:14:02.62,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,What am I so anxious about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.01,0:14:07.39,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,Kawabuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.39,0:14:09.30,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,Did you listen to the record I gave you yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.30,0:14:14.95,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Nah, I can't get into music that has girls squealin' over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.11,0:14:18.95,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,Isn't that the purpose of making music?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.95,0:14:21.05,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,Don't you wanna become popular?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.05,0:14:22.58,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Don't really care about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:25.77,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'm not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.77,0:14:27.63,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,Well, I wanna be popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:30.55,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,My dream is to become a star!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.94,0:14:32.76,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Huh? A star?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:34.56,apollon main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\c&H272A70&\bord1\shad0\fs38\3c&H0B0C1E&\fnRaysHand\b0\pos(823,551)\frz10.586}Seiji
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.16,0:14:38.42,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Wait a second! Are those the underpants of somebody who's aiming to be a star?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.42,0:14:39.64,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,Oh, these?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.64,0:14:42.81,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,I've got a lot of brothers, so if I don't stake my claim like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.81,0:14:44.36,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,they'll disappear in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.75,0:14:48.27,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,And we're poor, so we can't afford to buy new ones often.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.27,0:14:52.26,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,Amongst all my brothers, I'm called the "good-for-nothing."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.26,0:14:54.37,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,Really, singing is the only thing I'm good at.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.84,0:15:00.12,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,I wanna prove that I can become somebody who's able to support his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.42,0:15:06.42,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,To me, this band is the first step. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.89,0:15:10.62,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,Kawabuchi, I need your talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.41,0:15:30.78,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,A-Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.31,0:15:34.31,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,That was wonderful, Maruo! \NMuch better than I expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.31,0:15:35.49,apollon main,Yamaoka,0,0,0,,I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.79,0:15:39.20,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,All right, now all we need is a drummer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.56,0:15:43.08,apollon main,Yamaoka,0,0,0,,Seiji, are you gonna tell me who it is you have in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:47.14,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,Oh, you'll find out soon enough. \NBe ready for a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.61,0:15:50.76,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Hey, Ri'ko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.02,0:15:52.04,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.04,0:15:55.26,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,School's out tomorrow, so if you're free,\Nwanna go to the beach?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.40,0:15:58.02,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Ma told me to take the munchkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:16:02.27,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,But lookin' after them alone is a tough job,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.62,0:16:05.24,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,so I thought I'd ask you along to help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:09.13,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Well, if you're busy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.13,0:16:09.61,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.61,0:16:12.73,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Hold on there. You free tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.65,0:16:15.67,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,What do you say we have us a \Nclammin' contest at the sea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.67,0:16:17.26,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Huh? "Clamming"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.26,0:16:18.99,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Say, Sentaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.23,0:16:21.69,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I like clamming, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.69,0:16:22.50,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Ri...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:25.50,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,What's "clamming"? Is it some kind of competition?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.27,0:16:32.94,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Oh, Kaoru! Clamming means \Ndigging up clams at the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.93,0:16:35.97,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Oh! It's confusing when this guy \Ncalls it a contest or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.50,0:16:37.69,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Are you going too, Ri?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.62,0:16:39.45,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.45,0:16:40.43,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.88,0:16:44.02,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Then the threesome's set! \NThis is gonna be fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.14,0:16:48.39,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'll need to mentally prepare myself this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.39,0:16:52.64,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,If those two have a romantic moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.64,0:16:57.26,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'll casually get out of their way and just pray for Ri's happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.26,0:16:58.91,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,That was the idea,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.59,0:17:02.50,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,but maybe that's a non-issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.83,0:17:07.64,apollon main,Kota,0,0,0,,I got a hamaguri clam!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.64,0:17:09.38,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,That's a short-necked clam.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.38,0:17:13.30,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,Hi. Fancy meeting you here, Kawabuchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:15.13,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,Oh, it's a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.39,0:17:18.20,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,What cute little girls and boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.20,0:17:20.36,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,You know, you can find a ton of razor clams over there
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.36,0:17:21.27,apollon main,Kota,0,0,0,,Razors?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.27,0:17:23.86,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,You must be Ritsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.86,0:17:25.72,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,I've heard about you from Yurika.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.72,0:17:28.47,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,She said you were exceptionally cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:31.98,apollon main,Kota,0,0,0,,Hey! Where are the razor clams?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.22,0:17:34.98,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,Oh, they're right over here. Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:39.37,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,What's with that guy? \NSweet-talking everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.37,0:17:41.77,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Don't criticize the guy when you don't know 'im.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.17,0:17:44.75,apollon main,Kota,0,0,0,,Bro, you come too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,0:17:45.67,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.02,0:17:55.86,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,Pretty cool, right? Who wants to try it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.86,0:17:56.32,apollon main,Kota,0,0,0,,Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.32,0:17:57.39,apollon main,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Me, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.39,0:17:58.05,apollon main,Taiichi,0,0,0,,Salt!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.47,0:18:02.49,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Looks like they're having a good \Ntime over there. Shall we join them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.49,0:18:07.60,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'll pass. For some reason, that Matsuoka \Ncharacter rubs me the wrong way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.04,0:18:11.15,apollon main,Kota,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Taiichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.37,0:18:14.32,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Oh, no! I'll be back in a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.57,0:18:18.49,apollon main,Taiichi,0,0,0,,Crab!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.49,0:18:20.99,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,You were surprised when the \Ncrab pinched you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.37,0:18:22.88,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Thank goodness that's all it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.12,0:18:32.09,apollon main,Yamaoka,0,0,0,,Hey, Seiji! Don't tell me Kawabuchi's your drummer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.63,0:18:34.33,apollon main,Yamaoka,0,0,0,,Please, anybody but him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.33,0:18:36.65,apollon main,Maruo,0,0,0,,I-I'm against it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.65,0:18:40.30,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,He isn't as scary as you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:44.72,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,All I have to do is set him free from what's tying him down,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.27,0:18:47.33,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,and then everything should work out the way I want it to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.74,0:18:51.22,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Hey, Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.94,0:18:53.58,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Catchin' any short-necks?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.81,0:18:56.75,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Better not underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.75,0:18:58.99,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'm good at this kind of simple task.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.52,0:19:01.49,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Well, I ain't gonna lose either!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.49,0:19:02.41,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.41,0:19:04.22,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Clammin' contest!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.87,0:19:07.18,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,What do I get if I win?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.18,0:19:09.58,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,How about the record that Ri's dad gave you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:12.33,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Forget about it! 'Cause I'm gonna win anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:13.96,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,What about the Beatles record?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.99,0:19:19.12,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,Kawabuchi, did you listen to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:23.72,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Yeah, I heard it. Wasn't bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.38,0:19:26.02,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,Did it stir up your interest?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.02,0:19:28.77,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,I wouldn't go that far. But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.81,0:19:32.62,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,I'm thinkin' I'll help you out with
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.62,0:19:34.15,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,that band you're gonna have \Nfor the school festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:35.31,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.31,0:19:37.38,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,You'll join my rock band?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.38,0:19:37.99,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.99,0:19:38.94,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:42.02,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Richie, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.27,0:19:42.02,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,{\a6}I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.02,0:19:45.12,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,I'm just gonna be away 'til the festival's over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.83,0:19:48.41,apollon main,Boy,0,0,0,,We'll only be apart for a while, Nishimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.41,0:19:50.29,apollon main,Boy,0,0,0,,Let's send each other letters, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.79,0:19:54.71,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Fuck you!{orig: in a pig's ass! - dunno wtf...}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.89,0:19:57.63,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I was wrong about you, traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.91,0:20:04.02,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Richie, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.02,0:20:05.14,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.14,0:20:06.27,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.27,0:20:07.64,apollon main,,0,0,0,,I don't want to listen to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.87,0:20:12.10,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I don't need you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.09,0:20:17.69,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Kaoru! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.94,0:20:19.12,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Kaoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.21,0:20:29.66,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I know. I acted like an angry little kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.31,0:20:35.17,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,But being separated from him scares the hell out of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.09,0:20:38.67,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I abandoned him without thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.02,0:20:45.29,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Since coming here, I'd forgotten
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.29,0:20:47.60,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,that I'm not good at getting along with other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.82,0:20:50.09,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,It's better this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.75,0:20:53.85,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,After all, I've made it this far all on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.22,0:20:58.01,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,No problem... at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.89,0:21:05.07,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.07,0:21:07.05,apollon main,Bartender,0,0,0,,Tsutomu, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.01,0:21:09.53,apollon main,Bartender,0,0,0,,Look at the end of the counter!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.72,0:21:14.79,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,It can't be.
